videos.headline: Monte Morris assists Darrell Bowie's layup with a great pass in between traffic

videos.description: 2H (17:57) CIN Kyle Washington made Dunk. Assisted by Gary Clark.
videos.headline: Bounce pass leads to wide open dunk for Cincinnati

videos.description: 2H (12:58) ISU Deonte Burton made Three Point Jumper. Assisted by Monte Morris.
videos.headline: Deonte Burton makes fadeaway 3-Pointer to tie the game as the shot clock expires
Fastbreak layup gives Iowa State a 4 point lead

videos.description: 2H (5:33) CIN Kyle Washington made Two Point Tip Shot.
videos.headline: Cincinnati makes an and-one on 2nd chance shot to take the lead
Iowa State's guard goes coast to coast for the layin and the foul
Iowa State's lucky bounce results in a 3 point lead
Iowa State extends the lead with under two minutes left in the game

videos.description: With ten seconds left on the clock, Cincinnati ties the game at 50 with a jumper. Then, in the final seconds Iowa State's Nazareth Mitrou-Long is given the opportunity to win the game with a 3-pointer but misses, sending the game to overtime.
videos.headline: Wild sequence forces OT for Cincinnati-Iowa State

videos.description: OT (2:23) ISU Deonte Burton made Layup.
videos.headline: Defense leads to offense for Iowa State in overtime

videos.description: OT (0:05) ISU Nazareth Mitrou-Long missed Three Point Jumper.
videos.headline: Iowa State misses game-winning 3-Pointer in final seconds to fall to Cincinnati in Overtime
